1
00:00:02,830 --> 00:00:04,880
Joon Woo.

2
00:00:08,730 --> 00:00:11,500
Joon Woo, are you all right?

3
00:00:13,530 --> 00:00:15,660
Soo Bin.

4
00:00:17,220 --> 00:00:20,130
♬ Please don’t say a word ♬

5
00:00:20,130 --> 00:00:24,130
♬ Cuz they all have been said now ♬

6
00:00:24,130 --> 00:00:29,600
♬ Like a journey coming to an end ♬

7
00:00:29,600 --> 00:00:30,930
♬ You say ♬

8
00:00:30,930 --> 00:00:33,400
♬ Let it run like the river ♬

9
00:00:33,400 --> 00:00:35,870
♬ Wild and without a care ♬

10
00:00:35,870 --> 00:00:39,260
♬ Just like the days, ♬

11
00:00:39,260 --> 00:00:46,310
♬ we were young and fumbling ♬

12
00:00:46,310 --> 00:00:49,660
♬ Everything fades away ♬

13
00:00:49,660 --> 00:00:52,980
♬ Let it go by with a flow ♬

14
00:00:52,980 --> 00:00:56,360
♬ Really wish I could stay, ♬

15
00:00:56,360 --> 00:00:59,740
♬ but you know me ♬

16
00:01:00,690 --> 00:01:04,680
You're all grown up now, and I have a family.

17
00:01:04,680 --> 00:01:07,130
I think we each have different paths we have to take.

18
00:01:07,130 --> 00:01:10,510
You, in your own way, me, in my own way,

19
00:01:13,490 --> 00:01:15,090
♬ Just close your eyes ♬

20
00:01:15,090 --> 00:01:18,420
♬ and I'll be right by your side. ♬

21
00:01:18,420 --> 00:01:22,380
♬ Cuz memories don’t say goodbye ♬

22
00:01:27,100 --> 00:01:29,620
Where are you coming from?

23
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:53,630
What is he doing? What should I do?
What should I do? Please answer.

24
00:02:09,300 --> 00:02:13,050
I'm going to my friend Chan Yeol's house
to do some homework.

25
00:02:13,050 --> 00:02:15,220
Please take me.

26
00:02:16,570 --> 00:02:19,000
Hurry.

27
00:02:55,490 --> 00:02:59,050
Give me the ball, please.
Hurry!

28
00:03:06,960 --> 00:03:10,770
We aren't finished eating the jjajangmyeon
(black bean noodles).

29
00:03:21,480 --> 00:03:25,040
Thanks, jjajangmyeon Hyung.

30
00:03:25,040 --> 00:03:31,100
- You...
- A while ago you came to our house to get the empty bowls.

31
00:03:31,100 --> 00:03:35,820
- You have the best memory.
- It's because you're handsome.

32
00:03:39,570 --> 00:03:42,560
You're the one who's handsome.

33
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:46,400
I hear that a lot!

34
00:04:03,490 --> 00:04:07,640
Grow up with gusto, kiddo.

35
00:04:07,640 --> 00:04:09,910
Yes.

36
00:04:12,010 --> 00:04:14,420
Joon Woo.

37
00:04:14,420 --> 00:04:17,300
Mom!

38
00:04:17,300 --> 00:04:21,230
That hyung picked up the ball for me.

39
00:04:21,230 --> 00:04:26,080
Dad, let's have jjajangmyeon today.

40
00:04:27,730 --> 00:04:30,240
Go on in.

41
00:04:36,950 --> 00:04:41,740
- Bye, Jjajangmyeon Hyung.
- Thank you.

42
00:04:51,030 --> 00:04:53,490
What did you do?

43
00:04:54,770 --> 00:04:59,440
Why does the kid have the same name as me?
Why?

44
00:04:59,440 --> 00:05:02,760
When I named him, I thought that

45
00:05:02,760 --> 00:05:05,980
I wanted to somehow make atonement through that.

46
00:05:07,350 --> 00:05:12,690
Because I was so immature,
the things I didn't know then...

47
00:05:13,860 --> 00:05:18,740
While giving our kid everything and
raising him devotedly, at least in this way...

48
00:05:18,740 --> 00:05:21,940
Still, my name...

49
00:05:25,760 --> 00:05:31,050
Your sense of naming really... stinks.

50
00:05:35,900 --> 00:05:38,300
My mother

51
00:05:39,950 --> 00:05:43,430
still thinks the first love a long time ago

52
00:05:43,430 --> 00:05:47,560
was the most beautiful moment of her life.

53
00:05:50,400 --> 00:05:52,880
She always longs...

54
00:05:54,110 --> 00:05:56,680
for when she was 18.

55
00:05:59,740 --> 00:06:05,680
She always tells me, "our dad was such a good man."

56
00:06:06,670 --> 00:06:09,870
"He loved you so much."

57
00:06:11,280 --> 00:06:14,150
She always told me that.

58
00:06:18,670 --> 00:06:21,300
So I too

59
00:06:25,450 --> 00:06:30,800
yearned a lot for the person who is dad.

60
00:06:40,330 --> 00:06:43,660
I came because I didn't get to say this to you before.

61
00:06:44,540 --> 00:06:49,790
I am sorry, Joon Woo.
I am sorry.

62
00:06:49,790 --> 00:06:52,590
Don't worry.

63
00:06:54,100 --> 00:06:56,690
Now, I...

64
00:06:58,380 --> 00:07:01,830
I won't come looking for you again.

65
00:07:06,590 --> 00:07:10,830
- Be healthy.
- Joon Woo.

66
00:07:15,730 --> 00:07:19,840
- By chance, do you know Choi Myeong Joon?
- No. I don't know him.

67
00:07:19,840 --> 00:07:22,630
By chance, do you know Choi Myeong Joon?

68
00:07:22,630 --> 00:07:26,330
Choi Myeong Joon?
No.

69
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:32,300
Choi Myeong Joon.
Hello. I am Choi Joon Woo.

70
00:07:32,300 --> 00:07:37,680
Today is my birthday.
I wanted you to come see me.

71
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:44,800
But I'm okay because Mom
told me today's the happiest day for me.

72
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:50,670
Dad, I want to see you.
Let's meet someday?

73
00:07:50,670 --> 00:07:53,690
Hello. I'm Choi Joon Woo.

74
00:07:53,690 --> 00:07:57,990
I don't know what to say now that I'm doing this.

75
00:07:57,990 --> 00:08:02,610
Just... that I'm writing you
a letter to tell you that I yearned for you.

76
00:08:02,610 --> 00:08:07,170
I was always curious about
what kind of person my dad was.

77
00:08:07,170 --> 00:08:13,090
Occasionally, just occasionally,
I'll watch you from afar.

78
00:08:13,090 --> 00:08:18,320
Also, that I am Choi Joon Woo,
just remember that for me.

79
00:08:25,170 --> 00:08:27,890
Just the feeling of yearning...

80
00:08:27,890 --> 00:08:31,580
Just cherishing that feeling is enough.

81
00:08:31,580 --> 00:08:34,710
That feeling I used to feel...

82
00:08:42,060 --> 00:08:45,460
- Honey!
- How dare you come home now after wandering about?!

83
00:08:45,460 --> 00:08:50,520
After making a mess of the exams?
What? You made a joke out of the exams?

84
00:08:50,520 --> 00:08:53,850
There's no way you would have gotten it wrong
because you didn't know the answer. Are you crazy?

85
00:08:53,850 --> 00:08:57,080
You can just fix it for me again, though.

86
00:08:57,080 --> 00:09:02,650
That's right. Maybe Teacher Oh Han Gyeol
doesn't go for solicitations? What should we do then?

87
00:09:02,650 --> 00:09:08,580
- Hui Yeong!
- This punk, you're just dying to ruin me, aren't you?

88
00:09:08,580 --> 00:09:12,730
The money I earned while working like a dog,
you can't wait to squander it,

89
00:09:12,730 --> 00:09:16,340
- so you're just itching, huh?!
- Honey, honey! Please! Please!

90
00:09:16,340 --> 00:09:19,220
Please hit me instead!
Hit me!

91
00:09:19,220 --> 00:09:23,270
Fine, Park Geum Ja. Let's take care of you first.
All you do is drink while you're home.

92
00:09:23,270 --> 00:09:27,630
You leave that kid to turn out like that?
This—

93
00:09:27,630 --> 00:09:31,680
Let go. I said let go.
Let go! This dog-like...

94
00:09:31,680 --> 00:09:37,450
You're right. I'm a dog.
Just like you. Trash.

95
00:09:37,450 --> 00:09:41,340
What? This jerk!

96
00:09:41,340 --> 00:09:46,200
I hated you being like this since I was little.

97
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:50,200
I used to think I never wanted to be like you,

98
00:09:51,290 --> 00:09:56,380
but without realizing I was becoming just like you.

99
00:09:56,380 --> 00:09:59,640
Stepping on those who are weaker than me,

100
00:09:59,640 --> 00:10:04,120
a monster who uses whatever
method and means to get what I want.

101
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:09,070
Trash. I became that without a way to turn back.

102
00:10:09,920 --> 00:10:12,190
But you know what?

103
00:10:13,230 --> 00:10:17,010
I can't go back to when I wasn't like this.

104
00:10:17,880 --> 00:10:23,860
I wanted to be better than you! But I can't.

105
00:10:23,860 --> 00:10:26,810
- This jerk, how dare you, to your father?
- Honey, Honey.

106
00:10:26,810 --> 00:10:29,610
Let go. Let go!

107
00:10:33,510 --> 00:10:39,690
If you dare hit mom again, I won't let it slide.

108
00:10:48,950 --> 00:10:54,070
Go. Run away. Hurry.

109
00:11:22,420 --> 00:11:26,860
- Isn't this her?
- Oh wow, it is her. Kim Ji Min.

110
00:11:26,860 --> 00:11:30,480
- Isn't this that place?
- Why are you tracking her down for Teacher Oh Han Gyeol?

111
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:34,810
- Are you trying to bother her?
- No.

112
00:11:34,810 --> 00:11:38,150
I have my own reasons.

113
00:11:38,150 --> 00:11:41,870
- But why are we speaking so quietly?
- Hey.

114
00:11:47,530 --> 00:11:50,590
- Chan Yeol.
- Huh?

115
00:11:50,590 --> 00:11:55,900
- Let me use your phone for a sec.
- Sure. Here.

116
00:11:59,560 --> 00:12:03,080
Joon Woo, it's Yoo Soo Bin.
When you get to your job,

117
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:05,840
check the place where you park your bike for me.

118
00:12:05,840 --> 00:12:09,070
You have this one, too. Here.

119
00:12:21,530 --> 00:12:24,590
Oh, I'm so sleepy! Oh!

120
00:12:24,590 --> 00:12:27,620
- Soo Bin, come out and get some air, too!
- Soo Bin!

121
00:12:27,620 --> 00:12:30,660
Seriously, you're studying too hard!

122
00:12:30,660 --> 00:12:35,800
Oh, Unni! Unni!
Our Unni! Oh!

123
00:12:35,800 --> 00:12:38,230
Unni! Have you had dinner yet?

124
00:12:38,230 --> 00:12:40,770
Um... I'm okay.

125
00:12:40,770 --> 00:12:45,110
Aigoo, my grandma makes the best hot pot.

126
00:12:49,930 --> 00:12:52,400
I'll be right back. Thanks.

127
00:12:52,400 --> 00:12:57,560
- Yeah, be careful!
- Wow, I didn't expect her to be like that.

128
00:12:57,560 --> 00:13:02,400
That's true love.
Do you know what love is?

129
00:13:02,400 --> 00:13:04,960
Let's go.

130
00:13:35,520 --> 00:13:39,290
I said don't do it!

131
00:13:39,290 --> 00:13:43,040
Don't do it! Don't do it! Don't do it!

132
00:13:43,040 --> 00:13:48,410
Don't you dare meet up with Soo Bin or even call her!
I'm hanging up.

133
00:13:51,310 --> 00:13:53,880
Soo Bin.

134
00:13:55,060 --> 00:13:57,980
I was at Chan Yeol's to do homework together.

135
00:13:57,980 --> 00:14:01,240
- Oh, I heard.
- I'll go wash up.

136
00:14:01,240 --> 00:14:07,280
Okay.
Hey, why didn't you tell me you met Dad?

137
00:14:08,430 --> 00:14:14,130
Soo Bin.
Dad... I don't know what he said to you.

138
00:14:14,130 --> 00:14:18,450
But it's not true!
He's just made it up because we fought.

139
00:14:18,450 --> 00:14:22,020
- Don't worry about it, okay?
- Okay.

140
00:14:23,700 --> 00:14:28,900
I'm being serious.
We have no problems with each other at all!

141
00:14:28,900 --> 00:14:32,990
So you just have to study, that's all. Okay?

142
00:14:32,990 --> 00:14:35,510
Hey, we have to have a party to celebrate.
It's too late, right?

143
00:14:35,510 --> 00:14:39,880
So I was thinking.
How about a trip to Jejudo?

144
00:14:39,880 --> 00:14:45,420
- Whatever you want to do.
- Okay. I'll try and plan it out then.

145
00:14:46,350 --> 00:14:48,860
Okay.

146
00:15:23,280 --> 00:15:25,780
What are you doing?

147
00:15:32,450 --> 00:15:36,000
Is that funny?

148
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:41,760
No, I am.
That I'm hungry at a time like this.

149
00:15:57,000 --> 00:16:00,490
Joon Woo, it's Yoo Soo Bin.
When you get to your job,

150
00:16:00,490 --> 00:16:04,540
check the place where you park your bike for me.

151
00:16:55,670 --> 00:16:59,490
Joon Woo, you were surprised earlier, right?

152
00:16:59,490 --> 00:17:02,540
To be honest, Hui Yeong lent me his phone,

153
00:17:02,540 --> 00:17:06,530
so I called you out of urgency.

154
00:17:06,530 --> 00:17:11,900
But I happened to overhear, by chance,
that you were meeting up with that person.

155
00:17:11,900 --> 00:17:15,890
I'm sorry... without getting permission...

156
00:17:15,890 --> 00:17:19,050
You must be feeling bad.

157
00:17:19,050 --> 00:17:22,270
How you must have felt

158
00:17:22,270 --> 00:17:27,440
I know so well, so it upsets me.

159
00:17:28,190 --> 00:17:33,330
When I had a hard time with my dad,
you comforted me.

160
00:17:33,330 --> 00:17:36,530
I felt like I should do the same.

161
00:17:36,530 --> 00:17:39,800
But since I can't be with you,

162
00:17:39,800 --> 00:17:44,720
the only thing I can do for you
is send a letter like this.

163
00:17:44,720 --> 00:17:49,060
But I'm here for you.
I'm always cheering you on every day,

164
00:17:49,060 --> 00:17:54,280
in the morning, in the daytime,
when we're sleeping at night.

165
00:17:54,280 --> 00:18:00,290
So even with this little, let's try to bear it.

166
00:18:00,290 --> 00:18:05,700
I miss you, and I like you a lot.

167
00:18:05,700 --> 00:18:08,810
From Soo Bin.

168
00:19:04,130 --> 00:19:09,840
Ji Min, did you have a good day today and study a lot, too?

169
00:19:09,840 --> 00:19:14,490
Okay. Take your time and think about it.

170
00:19:14,490 --> 00:19:17,430
I'll wait.

171
00:19:23,150 --> 00:19:28,980
I have to wait until she feels okay.

172
00:20:42,490 --> 00:20:44,950
Sleep well.

173
00:21:00,350 --> 00:21:04,150
♬ The day on which a small door opened ♬

174
00:21:04,150 --> 00:21:09,340
♬ and the world changed ♬

175
00:21:09,340 --> 00:21:15,210
♬ was all about my feeling of happiness ♬

176
00:21:15,210 --> 00:21:18,770
♬ It is blindingly bright. ♬

177
00:21:18,770 --> 00:21:24,170
♬ I who am extending my insignificant hand ♬

178
00:21:24,170 --> 00:21:29,880
♬ cautiously express hello with feeling ♬

179
00:21:31,490 --> 00:21:36,560
♬ On another quiet afternoon ♬

180
00:21:40,860 --> 00:21:42,480
I...

181
00:21:43,310 --> 00:21:46,320
will try to do better,

182
00:21:46,320 --> 00:21:49,920
so that I can be a more dependable person to you.

183
00:21:51,830 --> 00:21:54,610
Sleep well.

184
00:22:05,480 --> 00:22:08,080
Are you on a diet?

185
00:22:08,080 --> 00:22:12,860
Kwon Da Huin's always on a diet.
And you're her boyfriend.

186
00:22:17,240 --> 00:22:19,370
Ma Hui Yeong.

187
00:22:21,610 --> 00:22:23,870
Eat.

188
00:22:25,220 --> 00:22:27,930
You didn't use to be like this.

189
00:22:29,000 --> 00:22:32,070
Why have you changed so much?

190
00:22:36,600 --> 00:22:40,680
Enjoy it.
I'm leaving.

191
00:22:47,160 --> 00:22:49,640
Jeong Oh Je, hi!

192
00:22:52,050 --> 00:22:54,330
You're here?

193
00:23:01,480 --> 00:23:05,990
Why are you so out of energy?
You said you made up with Da Huin.

194
00:23:05,990 --> 00:23:09,960
Yeah. We did.

195
00:23:14,410 --> 00:23:17,560
Should we talk for a sec?

196
00:23:17,560 --> 00:23:19,890
Okay.

197
00:23:22,500 --> 00:23:27,830
I should have told you first. Sorry.

198
00:23:29,970 --> 00:23:34,650
You didn't have to tell me.
It's your choice.

199
00:23:38,430 --> 00:23:41,650
I'm weird, aren't I?

200
00:23:41,650 --> 00:23:45,350
No. It's just how you feel.

201
00:23:46,420 --> 00:23:49,250
True.

202
00:23:51,100 --> 00:23:58,000
I'm a little confused, too,
about what kind of feelings these are,

203
00:23:59,010 --> 00:24:02,590
so I was in the process of figuring it out myself.

204
00:24:02,590 --> 00:24:06,310
But then it turned out this way.

205
00:24:12,080 --> 00:24:15,070
Hui Yeong.
Thanks.

206
00:24:15,070 --> 00:24:18,200
You got to make the call?

207
00:24:18,200 --> 00:24:21,240
I didn't pick up thinking it was you.

208
00:24:25,520 --> 00:24:28,280
I got it last night, thanks.

209
00:24:47,340 --> 00:24:51,420
- Really?
- What is this? It's weird.

210
00:24:51,420 --> 00:24:57,230
Hey. What's weird?
It's a person liking another person.

211
00:24:57,230 --> 00:25:04,250
- You're the weirder. Just play your game.
- Oh, Yoo Pil Sang, so unexpected!

212
00:25:10,610 --> 00:25:14,070
Did you see it, Hui Yeong?

213
00:25:16,660 --> 00:25:20,150
(Texts about Oh Je)

214
00:25:43,700 --> 00:25:46,770
- What page are we on?
- I don't know.

215
00:25:49,990 --> 00:25:53,800
You know, Jeong Oh Je and Kwon Da Huin—

216
00:25:53,800 --> 00:25:57,780
Eun Seo Jin! Shut up!
That thing...

217
00:25:57,780 --> 00:26:01,320
It's fine. Leave her alone.
She'll probably stop.

218
00:26:01,320 --> 00:26:04,090
Hey, don't get bothered.

219
00:26:05,250 --> 00:26:09,780
Da Huin, you're okay, right?

220
00:26:19,940 --> 00:26:26,950
Hey, Jeong Oh Je! What happened? You said we were gonna come to school together. You said you'd carry my plant for me!

221
00:26:26,950 --> 00:26:33,200
Oh, sorry. I had to babysit because my parents
had to go to the market in the morning.

222
00:26:34,300 --> 00:26:37,420
Follow me.
There are so many things you need to carry for me.

223
00:26:37,420 --> 00:26:40,570
Guys, we are going to the horticulture room.

224
00:26:49,130 --> 00:26:51,470
Go ahead.

225
00:26:55,130 --> 00:26:57,610
- Oh Je.
- Huh?

226
00:26:57,610 --> 00:27:02,210
Don't be sorry towards me.
You don't need to be.

227
00:27:03,510 --> 00:27:09,350
Also, don't make faces like that.
You look the nicest when you smile. Smile.

228
00:27:11,940 --> 00:27:15,800
- Okay.
- Go.

229
00:27:21,290 --> 00:27:25,980
Kwon Da Huin, what's up with you?
Heart's fluttering still.

230
00:27:30,140 --> 00:27:34,840
Class 2-3's male student, Jeong Oh Je,
likes grade manipulator, Ma Hui Yeong. Is this real?

231
00:27:45,120 --> 00:27:48,600
Yeah, Joon Woo.

232
00:27:49,460 --> 00:27:54,140
- Teach.
- Something going on?

233
00:27:59,030 --> 00:28:04,400
Why are you so serious?
You're making me nervous. Go on and tell me.

234
00:28:04,400 --> 00:28:10,100
I... visited an academy.

235
00:28:10,100 --> 00:28:12,250
Why?

236
00:28:13,200 --> 00:28:16,550
The... ladybug...

237
00:28:16,550 --> 00:28:22,490
Ladybug Academy... does what there?

238
00:28:22,490 --> 00:28:26,810
- Drawings.
- Drawings?

239
00:28:31,130 --> 00:28:34,220
Drawings, then by chance...

240
00:28:34,220 --> 00:28:40,290
You're saying you're going to decide on the path to take?

241
00:28:41,970 --> 00:28:48,100
Drawing, art, art college.

242
00:28:50,020 --> 00:28:54,780
Hooray!
Hooray! Hooray.

243
00:28:54,780 --> 00:28:58,970
