248
00:29:14,200 --> 00:29:18,490
But still, you should study it a little more systematically.

249
00:29:18,490 --> 00:29:22,920
Yes. So I am looking into a few places,

250
00:29:22,920 --> 00:29:27,100
but it's not so easy.

251
00:29:30,700 --> 00:29:33,140
Right.

252
00:29:34,410 --> 00:29:39,070
Oh right, my successor in the army runs
an art preparatory academy.

253
00:29:39,070 --> 00:29:41,900
