254
00:29:42,640 --> 00:29:45,300
He's not as good looking as me, but still,

255
00:29:45,300 --> 00:29:49,970
it seems like he's a little bit well-known
in terms of prepping for art colleges.

256
00:29:50,640 --> 00:29:54,770
Right, prepping for art colleges isn't so easy.

257
00:29:55,790 --> 00:29:59,470
But still, I'll help you.

258
00:30:01,460 --> 00:30:04,860
