259
00:30:04,860 --> 00:30:07,320
It's alright.

260
00:30:08,590 --> 00:30:11,470
Thank you.

261
00:30:13,610 --> 00:30:16,820
I'll let him know, so go see him at the academy.

262
00:30:16,820 --> 00:30:20,020
You have to do these sorts of things
right away as soon as you get the feeling.

263
00:30:20,020 --> 00:30:23,780
Joon Woo, let's go for it, huh?!

264
00:30:30,950 --> 00:30:33,510
Soo Bin.

265
00:30:38,040 --> 00:30:41,120
You didn't sleep well last night?

266
00:30:42,110 --> 00:30:46,150
I couldn't sleep well after reading your letter.

267
00:30:46,150 --> 00:30:48,580
Because I was so touched.

268
00:30:49,630 --> 00:30:51,720
It's nothing.

269
00:30:51,720 --> 00:30:55,760
I thought about what I could do for you,

270
00:30:55,760 --> 00:30:58,250
and that was the only thing.

271
00:30:59,840 --> 00:31:02,610
Should we do that the next time we have things to say?

272
00:31:02,610 --> 00:31:07,140
Sometimes...
when it feels too overwhelming to put into words?

273
00:31:11,590 --> 00:31:13,930
Soo Bin.

274
00:31:14,840 --> 00:31:20,370
- I have a goal now. What to do in the future.
- Like what?

275
00:31:20,370 --> 00:31:25,160
It's not specific yet, but since I like drawing,

276
00:31:26,190 --> 00:31:29,480
I'm going to study with that as my goal.

277
00:31:29,480 --> 00:31:33,390
Really?
Good job.

278
00:31:33,390 --> 00:31:37,800
I really like your drawing, too.

279
00:31:37,800 --> 00:31:40,990
I'll cheer you on sincerely.

280
00:31:42,760 --> 00:31:48,600
It's thanks to you.
Because of you, I've decided to live a better life

281
00:31:49,800 --> 00:31:52,510
and have a dream, too.

282
00:31:52,510 --> 00:32:00,610
You... changed a lot. I'm proud of you.

283
00:32:00,610 --> 00:32:04,530
Right? Oh, right.

284
00:32:04,530 --> 00:32:07,060
What is it?

285
00:32:07,060 --> 00:32:10,700
I promised not to meet privately with you like this.

286
00:32:15,400 --> 00:32:18,190
