287
00:32:20,320 --> 00:32:24,660
- Go ahead.
- Okay.

288
00:32:28,650 --> 00:32:30,440
Joon Woo.

289
00:32:31,560 --> 00:32:36,790
You... are really a good person.

290
00:32:48,080 --> 00:32:49,770
So Ye.

291
00:32:51,350 --> 00:32:55,730
