292
00:32:55,730 --> 00:32:57,340
You have something to say?

293
00:32:57,340 --> 00:33:00,060
To thank you for the other day in front of Sang Hoon.

294
00:33:00,060 --> 00:33:03,460
Okay. I'll get going.

295
00:33:04,570 --> 00:33:06,340
So Ye.

296
00:33:07,680 --> 00:33:11,450
I'm really trying hard to be an honorable person to you.

297
00:33:11,450 --> 00:33:14,200
So please give me one more chance.

298
00:33:15,570 --> 00:33:18,970
Give me one more chance.

299
00:33:19,780 --> 00:33:22,860
Did you do well on the exams?

300
00:33:34,440 --> 00:33:36,640
Aren't you going to take this?

301
00:33:40,990 --> 00:33:44,090
I heard about you.

302
00:33:44,090 --> 00:33:48,470
It's your choice, but don't get me involved.

303
00:33:49,720 --> 00:33:52,920
Don't worry. It will never happen.

304
00:33:52,920 --> 00:33:55,080
It's just my issue.

305
00:33:58,840 --> 00:34:04,450
Teacher, by chance, is there anyone you know
who works in the field of prepping for art colleges?

306
00:34:04,450 --> 00:34:05,990
Teacher Oh!

307
00:34:05,990 --> 00:34:08,140
Teacher Oh! There's a huge problem.

308
00:34:08,140 --> 00:34:10,290
Please go on ahead.

309
00:34:13,690 --> 00:34:16,990
