310
00:34:18,680 --> 00:34:21,100
Ah, daebak!

311
00:34:21,100 --> 00:34:23,880
People from the Office of Education
came because of Ma Hui Yeong.

312
00:34:23,880 --> 00:34:25,580
Daebak!

313
00:34:35,030 --> 00:34:37,990
Let me! Let me see!

314
00:34:43,100 --> 00:34:48,600
Hey! What are you guys doing!
Get back to class! Hurry.

315
00:34:51,700 --> 00:34:53,990
Sang Hoon, go! Quickly.

316
00:34:53,990 --> 00:34:57,520
Okay. I will.

317
00:35:01,110 --> 00:35:07,180
Ma Hui Yeong, did you know about the grade manipulation
that happened during the second semester of last year?

318
00:35:08,160 --> 00:35:13,490
