During that time, Hui Yeong himself didn't know—

319
00:35:15,750 --> 00:35:18,490
Let's have Ma Hui Yeong tell us.

320
00:35:20,980 --> 00:35:23,850
I just found out recently.

321
00:35:25,720 --> 00:35:28,110
I acknowledge everything.

322
00:35:28,810 --> 00:35:31,430
I'll cooperate with the investigation.

323
00:35:34,200 --> 00:35:40,200
If the grade manipulation is proven to have happened,
you and the teachers involved

324
00:35:40,200 --> 00:35:44,930
and your parents will receive punishment.

325
00:35:44,930 --> 00:35:46,820
Finally,

326
00:35:47,690 --> 00:35:51,420
you will receive zero grades accordingly.

327
