Hey.
Aren't you relieved?

328
00:36:31,710 --> 00:36:32,800
Was it you?

329
00:36:32,800 --> 00:36:36,300
What?
You think it was me? Oh wow.

330
00:36:37,620 --> 00:36:42,240
I should have been, but sadly, it wasn't.

331
00:36:44,280 --> 00:36:46,060
I'm being serious!

332
00:36:46,060 --> 00:36:50,610
