Love-hate became friendship or what?

333
00:36:54,980 --> 00:36:57,240
I'm so glad.

334
00:36:58,680 --> 00:37:02,930
If he's guilty, he should be punished.

335
00:37:04,060 --> 00:37:06,190
I thought it was you, that's all.

336
00:37:29,630 --> 00:37:32,590
Hello?
Dad, it's Sang Hoon.

337
00:37:39,910 --> 00:37:41,860
Are you nuts?

338
00:37:43,060 --> 00:37:45,680
Don't be ridiculous!

339
00:37:54,950 --> 00:37:58,010
Variability means it can be chance.

340
00:37:58,010 --> 00:38:01,400
Technical level which uses variability or

341
00:38:10,730 --> 00:38:14,620
for example, in the past,
we didn't have the technical ability to use bacteria,

342
00:38:14,620 --> 00:38:17,410
so it was just a natural object, but how is it now?

343
00:38:17,410 --> 00:38:20,000
It's become a very important resource.

344
00:38:20,000 --> 00:38:22,430
It means it's worth changing this way.

345
00:38:22,430 --> 00:38:24,470
Also, the resource—

346
00:38:27,800 --> 00:38:31,400
- Vice Principal.
- Teacher Oh.

347
00:38:31,460 --> 00:38:35,470
How could something like this
happen without my knowing?

348
00:38:36,550 --> 00:38:40,920
Something scandalous like this happening
in all my 25 years as an educator...

349
00:38:41,640 --> 00:38:43,380
