I can't become a principal...

351
00:38:46,290 --> 00:38:48,050
No, no, no. No way.

352
00:38:48,050 --> 00:38:52,590
Do your best with the investigation and finish it up well.

353
00:38:57,020 --> 00:39:00,200
I've devoted so many years to this school.

354
00:39:00,200 --> 00:39:02,220
No way it would happen.

355
00:39:14,360 --> 00:39:18,770
Teach, there's something I'd like to consult with you about.

356
00:39:20,900 --> 00:39:25,250
Consult? I'm okay anytime.
Right now? Here in school?

357
00:39:25,250 --> 00:39:28,680
I'd like to meet you outside of school.

358
00:39:30,090 --> 00:39:32,850
Sure, sure. Where?

359
00:39:37,000 --> 00:39:41,880
Chan Yeol, I just got here.
You're not here yet?

360
00:39:43,620 --> 00:39:47,120
Teach! Have you met up with that unni?

361
00:39:49,300 --> 00:39:52,230
This kid... You're asking for trouble.

362
00:39:56,860 --> 00:39:58,880
Ji Min...

363
00:40:01,080 --> 00:40:04,530
