370
00:40:29,480 --> 00:40:33,450
Why do you say such a thing?
That's not true.

371
00:40:34,150 --> 00:40:37,230
I'm sorry. I'll be going in now.

372
00:40:37,230 --> 00:40:40,560
Enjoy the drink. Good-bye.

373
00:40:40,560 --> 00:40:42,710
