374
00:40:50,630 --> 00:40:54,200
Thanks, Chan Yeol.
I met up with her.

375
00:40:55,830 --> 00:40:59,230
Please do well this time, Teach.

376
00:41:02,140 --> 00:41:04,500
What's wrong with my eyes?

377
00:41:19,120 --> 00:41:21,650
Why would she say...

378
00:41:23,470 --> 00:41:29,270
