Why is it so complicated?

379
00:41:54,390 --> 00:41:56,630
What are you doing?

380
00:41:56,630 --> 00:41:59,020
Oh right, you're working.

381
00:41:59,020 --> 00:42:01,330
It was me after all.

382
00:42:02,340 --> 00:42:06,460
Whistle-blower. It was me.

383
00:42:12,090 --> 00:42:15,530
I called my dad earlier from school because I got a feeling.

384
00:42:15,530 --> 00:42:18,290
He reported it.

385
00:42:18,290 --> 00:42:23,470
Why would he dig up the past now?

386
00:42:23,470 --> 00:42:28,780
What about his job?
Wasn't that why you held back?

387
00:42:28,780 --> 00:42:30,380
He quit his job.

388
00:42:30,380 --> 00:42:33,980
He has nothing to lose now,
so he says he can do whatever he wants.

389
00:42:33,980 --> 00:42:39,880
Then he should have told me.
Why would he quit his job and stuff?

390
00:42:41,560 --> 00:42:45,140
If he had told me back then, Hui Yeong...
I don't know. I don't know.

391
00:42:45,140 --> 00:42:48,160
It's good. It's a good thing.

392
00:42:48,160 --> 00:42:50,320
Oh, I'm so relieved! Seriously.

393
00:42:51,820 --> 00:42:54,230
Why? What?

394
00:42:54,230 --> 00:42:56,450
You don't feel good, right?

395
00:42:57,690 --> 00:42:59,260
No. No.

396
00:42:59,260 --> 00:43:02,260
I-I feel so good.

397
00:43:02,260 --> 00:43:04,100
I'm so relieved. So, so relieved.

398
00:43:11,350 --> 00:43:14,310
It's already happened.

399
00:43:15,760 --> 00:43:18,050
Leave now.

400
00:43:18,050 --> 00:43:21,280
Okay. I should.

401
00:43:23,470 --> 00:43:24,800
Choi Joon Woo.

402
00:43:24,800 --> 00:43:26,600
Lee Gi Tae, what are you doing here?

403
00:43:26,600 --> 00:43:27,980
By chance, have you seen Hui Yeong?

404
00:43:27,980 --> 00:43:31,500
This jerk is obsessed with him again!

405
00:43:32,670 --> 00:43:34,270
No, he's being strange.

406
00:43:34,270 --> 00:43:38,710
