he was sorry and I can't contact him.

407
00:43:38,710 --> 00:43:40,860
The academy said he quit.

408
00:43:42,030 --> 00:43:43,860
So?

409
00:43:45,260 --> 00:43:49,370
Well... I wondered if he stopped by here.

410
00:43:49,370 --> 00:43:51,130
I'll leave.

411
00:43:57,800 --> 00:43:59,650
Go then.

412
00:43:59,650 --> 00:44:01,460
I'm leaving.

413
00:44:23,660 --> 00:44:25,610
Let's try and find him at least.

414
00:44:26,590 --> 00:44:28,720
