415
00:44:28,720 --> 00:44:29,810
It's raining, too.

416
00:44:29,810 --> 00:44:31,130
I feel so uneasy.

417
00:44:31,130 --> 00:44:34,020
- His phone is off, too.
- Maybe something's happened.

418
00:44:34,020 --> 00:44:37,510
What do you mean?!
Stop being so rash!

419
00:44:42,620 --> 00:44:44,880
Yeah, Oh Je.

420
00:44:44,880 --> 00:44:46,780
Yeah, what are you doing?

421
00:44:46,780 --> 00:44:48,570
Oh, I...

422
00:44:49,560 --> 00:44:54,310
Hui Yeong?
He'll go home himself.

423
00:45:04,200 --> 00:45:09,300
Finally, you will receive a grade of zero.

424
00:45:17,320 --> 00:45:21,130
That bastard.
