427
00:45:30,930 --> 00:45:36,050
He still hasn't learned. It's enough knowing
that he's okay. Let's go.

428
00:45:39,850 --> 00:45:43,200
Just let me be trash and let me get destroyed!

429
00:45:43,200 --> 00:45:47,900
