Are you happy seeing me break into pieces, too?

430
00:45:47,900 --> 00:45:52,390
Are you having fun?
I said to leave, you bastard!

431
00:45:55,790 --> 00:45:57,940
You guys go home.

432
00:46:02,770 --> 00:46:05,480
Hey, Lee Gi Tae, let's go!

433
00:46:12,180 --> 00:46:15,790
