Making the guys worry.

434
00:46:15,790 --> 00:46:18,080
What do you care?

435
00:46:19,080 --> 00:46:21,930
You're a coward even now.

436
00:46:21,930 --> 00:46:24,200
Are you trying to be forgiven this way?

437
00:46:24,200 --> 00:46:26,820
I have no intention of being forgiven.

438
00:46:29,130 --> 00:46:31,560
You and your pride even now...

439
00:46:33,690 --> 00:46:36,500
Then why are you so tormented?

440
00:46:37,240 --> 00:46:41,620
Saying the word "sorry"
to me hurts your pride that much?

441
00:46:43,160 --> 00:46:47,320
Is it that hard to acknowledge your mistake?

442
00:46:49,800 --> 00:46:53,000
Do you know why I've just been watching you?

443
00:46:54,300 --> 00:46:57,050
Because I feel really sorry for you.

444
00:47:02,670 --> 00:47:09,120
You acting this way right now,
you feel tormented because you know were wrong.

445
00:47:11,270 --> 00:47:13,640
Don't avoid it and resolve it.

446
00:47:13,640 --> 00:47:17,820
Take responsibility and fix it yourself.

447
00:47:18,780 --> 00:47:21,470
Don't be such a coward.

448
00:47:26,140 --> 00:47:28,260
It's your last chance.

449
00:47:46,760 --> 00:47:49,420
This is your birthday?

450
00:47:49,420 --> 00:47:51,430
Yeah.

451
00:47:51,430 --> 00:47:54,840
It wasn't on the school's bulletin board.

452
00:47:54,840 --> 00:47:58,300
Oh, that's because my mom reported my birth late.

453
00:48:00,550 --> 00:48:04,700
I'll take care of your birthday this time no matter what.

454
00:48:04,700 --> 00:48:07,330
Okay. I am looking forward to it.

455
00:48:09,680 --> 00:48:11,050
Joon Woo's birthday

456
00:48:11,050 --> 00:48:13,870
It's his birthday today...

457
00:48:38,680 --> 00:48:40,900
- Did you just go home?
- Yeah.

458
00:48:51,180 --> 00:48:53,090
Guys.

459
00:48:54,340 --> 00:48:56,670
I have something to say.

460
00:48:58,270 --> 00:49:01,660
Today I'll tell Teach that I won't be president anymore.

461
00:49:01,660 --> 00:49:05,130
I don't need to tell you why I'm not fit to be one.

462
00:49:05,130 --> 00:49:10,350
From now on,
I think Joon Woo will do a great job with class management.

463
00:49:11,710 --> 00:49:14,180
I'm sorry for not being able to finish off the term.

464
00:49:15,600 --> 00:49:19,030
Hey, hey. President Ma,
why are you making the decision by yourself?

465
00:49:19,030 --> 00:49:21,900
You should ask for our opinions, too.

466
00:49:28,880 --> 00:49:31,250
I don't think there's a need.

467
00:49:57,070 --> 00:50:01,430
Hui Yeong. Let's talk.

