475
00:50:24,590 --> 00:50:29,650
But since we're still friends, we can't ignore it.

476
00:50:31,330 --> 00:50:33,380
It's because it's summer.

477
00:50:36,020 --> 00:50:38,120
I'm fine.

478
00:50:38,120 --> 00:50:39,940
Hui Yeong.

479
00:50:39,940 --> 00:50:42,020
Thanks for worrying about me.

480
00:50:48,630 --> 00:50:49,980
Let her be.

481
00:50:49,980 --> 00:50:54,660
Just let him go around proudly, just like his concept.

482
00:50:55,600 --> 00:50:58,360
Don't worry too much about it now.

483
00:50:58,360 --> 00:51:02,100
That's right. Just protect your love.

484
00:51:05,320 --> 00:51:08,640
Guys, can I ask a favor?

485
00:51:09,500 --> 00:51:11,290
What is it?

486
00:51:12,770 --> 00:51:16,080
Honestly, today is Choi Joon Woo's birthday.

487
00:51:16,080 --> 00:51:21,710
I have a gift that I thought about.
I will buy it so will you please give it to him?

488
00:51:21,710 --> 00:51:23,820
Yoo Soo Bin, you coward.

489
00:51:23,820 --> 00:51:26,290
Can't you even give a birthday gift personally?

490
00:51:26,290 --> 00:51:29,630
If you're going to be like that then quit it...
with Choi Joon Woo.

491
00:51:29,630 --> 00:51:33,500
